{"doc":{"isMarkdown":true,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"CSS 預處理器","mdn_url":"/zh-TW/docs/Glossary/CSS_preprocessor","locale":"zh-TW","native":"正體中文 (繁體)","sidebarHTML":"","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p><strong>CSS 預處理器</strong>是個能透過該預處理器語法，產生純 <a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/Glossary/CSS\">CSS</a> 的程式。CSS 預處理器有很多選擇，不過大多數的 CSS 預處理器都會添加純 CSS 所沒有的功能，例如：mixin、巢狀選擇器、繼承選擇器等。這些功能會令 CSS 結構的可讀性更高、也更容易維護。</p>\n<p>要使用 CSS 預處理器，你需要在<a class=\"page-not-created\" title=\"The documentation about this has not yet been written; please consider contributing!\">伺服器</a>安裝 CSS 編譯器，或是在開發環境透過 CSS 預處理器編譯後，上傳編譯好的 CSS 到伺服器。</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"參見","title":"參見","isH3":false,"content":"<ul>\n  <li>以下列出幾個最受歡迎的 CSS 預處理器：\n    <ul>\n      <li><a href=\"https://sass-lang.com/\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">Sass</a></li>\n      <li><a href=\"https://lesscss.org/\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">LESS</a></li>\n      <li><a href=\"https://stylus-lang.com/\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">Stylus</a></li>\n      <li><a href=\"https://postcss.org/\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">PostCSS</a></li>\n    </ul>\n  </li>\n  <li><a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/Glossary\">MDN 術語表</a>\n    <ul>\n      <li><a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/Glossary/CSS\">CSS</a></li>\n    </ul>\n  </li>\n</ul>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"參見","id":"參見"}],"summary":"CSS 預處理器是個能透過該預處理器語法，產生純 CSS 的程式。CSS 預處理器有很多選擇，不過大多數的 CSS 預處理器都會添加純 CSS 所沒有的功能，例如：mixin、巢狀選擇器、繼承選擇器等。這些功能會令 CSS 結構的可讀性更高、也更容易維護。","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-10-01T03:41:16.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"CSS preprocessor","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"Preprocesador CSS","locale":"es","native":"Español"},{"title":"Préprocesseur CSS","locale":"fr","native":"Français"},{"title":"CSS preprocessor (CSS プリプロセッサー)","locale":"ja","native":"日本語"},{"title":"CSS 전처리기","locale":"ko","native":"한국어"},{"title":"Pré-processador CSS","locale":"pt-BR","native":"Português (d